### Extend SEO Fields (TypeScript)

Source: https://github.com/payloadcms/payload/blob/main/docs/plugins/seo.mdx

Customize the default meta fields provided by the SEO plugin. This example shows how to use the `fields` option to add a new custom text field named 'customField' to the meta field group.

```typescript
// payload.config.ts
{
  // ...
  seoPlugin({
    fields: ({ defaultFields }) => [
      ...defaultFields,
      {
        name: 'customField',
        type: 'text',
      },
    ],
  })
}
```

